thread.title_full: Otticanet recensione scritta da craig andrews

author: craig andrews
title: craig andrews
text: I was very happy with the service otticanet provided with my order they dispatched my order the next day and sent me a detailed account and tracking information i placed my order on wednesday and my order was delivered to my address is sydney on monday ! I purchased a pair of seringeti sunglasses and otticanet were by far the cheapest supplier i could find and they also offered am extra 5% doscount at my time of purchase will buy from them again in the future
